@startuml state-church-account
title Church Account — State Diagram

[*] --> Applied : Church submits application

Applied --> PendingApproval : Admin begins review

PendingApproval --> Active : Admin approves
PendingApproval --> Applied : Admin requests\nmore information

Active --> Suspended : Policy violation\nor admin action
Suspended --> Active : Admin reactivates
Suspended --> Deactivated : Prolonged suspension\nor church request

Active --> Deactivated : Church requests\ndeactivation

Deactivated --> [*]

note right of Active
  Church has access to:
  - Custom branding
  - Playlist curation
  - Engagement analytics
end note

note right of Suspended
  All church features
  disabled. Playlists
  hidden from public.
end note

note right of Deactivated
  Data retained for
  30 days, then purged.
end note

@enduml
